Shock and fear have gripped Ol Jabet Shopping centre in Laikipia County after a businessman was hacked to death by unknown people.
The businessman identified as Mr Patrick Maina is the latest casualty following a spate of attacks in the area in the past few months.
Residents found his body by a road on Saturday morning, covered in blood and with deep cuts in the head and back.



